"children":[
"Treatment"
]
},
"children":[
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"19eb50",
"children":[
"Select nonsedating antihistamines as first-line therapy."
]
},
{
"type":"heading",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
"Don't Be Tricked"
]
},
{
"type":"list",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"ed80f5",
"children":[
"Measurement of C1 inhibitor levels is not indicated in patients with urticaria, because C1 inhibitor deficiency, seen in hereditary angioedema, is not associated with hives."
]
},
" "
]
},
{
